HEADWORD: Impair
<hw>Im"pair</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>impair</ets>
uneven, L. <ets>impar</ets>; <ets>im-</ets> not + <ets>par</ets>
equal.]</ety> <def>Not fit or appropriate.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Impair</ent>⟦br⟧

